sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Gateway/EPP)
    participant Proxy as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant Allowlist as Allowlist Validator<br/>(SSRF Protection)
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller Pod<br/>dynamic port
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port<br/>Header: x-request-id<br/>HTTPS/8000 TLS 1.2+

        opt SSRF Protection Enabled
            Proxy->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller target
            Allowlist-->>Proxy: Allowed / 403 Forbidden
        end

        Proxy->>Prefiller: Forward request to prefiller<br/>HTTP(S)/dynamic port<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
        Note right of Prefiller: Computes KV cache<br/>for prompt tokens

        Prefiller-->>Proxy: Response with kv_transfer_params<br/>{do_remote_decode, do_remote_prefill,<br/>remote_block_ids, remote_engine_id,<br/>remote_host, remote_port}

        Note over Proxy: Extract kv_transfer_params<br/>from prefiller response,<br/>merge into decoder request

        Proxy->>Decoder: Forward enriched request<br/>with kv_transfer_params<br/>HTTP(S)/8001<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
        Note right of Decoder: Generates tokens using<br/>transferred KV cache

        Decoder-->>Proxy: Inference response<br/>(streaming or complete)
        Proxy-->>Client: Forward response<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Decode (No Prefiller)
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port header)<br/>HTTPS/8000 TLS 1.2+

        Note over Proxy: No prefiller header detected<br/>Route directly to decoder

        Proxy->>Decoder: Forward request unchanged<br/>HTTP(S)/8001<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
        Decoder-->>Proxy: Inference response
        Proxy-->>Client: Forward response<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 3: Passthrough (Non-intercepted paths)
        Client->>Proxy: GET /v1/models<br/>HTTPS/8000 TLS 1.2+

        Note over Proxy: Path not intercepted<br/>Transparent passthrough

        Proxy->>Decoder: Forward unchanged<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
        Decoder-->>Proxy: Response
        Proxy-->>Client: Forward response
    end
